Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.37,0:15:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go to the next slide then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.44,0:15:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember what they were.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.67,0:15:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're going to contrast these two realms.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.03,0:15:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The great scientists of history in the 400s all the way up to 499.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Freud was at 499.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.36,0:15:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Einstein, a great many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The great geniuses of science were at 499.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Isaac Newton, 499.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.34,0:16:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.44,0:16:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's that paradigm of the 400s.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It stops at 499.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.96,0:16:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of them in their personal life were quite devoted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was not in their public work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.79,0:16:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That was in their private life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual teachers, on the other hand, this is their public life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.54,0:16:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Their work life is the same as their personal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.52,0:16:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're familiar with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.30,0:16:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This list, it's in the book, and I tend to repeat it in the books I'm writing subsequently so that people don't have to flip back and look in some other book and look for the page.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.71,0:16:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So when it's convenient in the book I'm writing now, I just repeat this, and I just say repeated for convenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But these are the great names that we know throughout history.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.54,0:17:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'll see they tend to be somewhere in the high 400s, but then they're almost all in the 500s.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.36,0:17:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And the most erudite, the great sage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.43,0:17:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The great sages are really in like 700, are the great sages.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The great avatars, Jesus Christ and Buddha, are in 1,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.42,0:17:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So here we see James Allen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.51,0:17:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Not everybody's familiar with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He teaches non-duality.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we have the great names of spirituality, Aurobindo, Annie Vison, Wallace Black Elk, Bodhidharma, Jacob Bohm, Richard Buck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.09,0:17:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Swami Buddha Nanda, Eric Butterworth, a very well-known teacher, Ram Chandra, Confucius, the current Dalai Lama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.23,0:17:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Dalai Lama and the popes tend to be, Dalai Lama tend to calibrate about the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.43,0:18:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The level of sainthood is around 570, and the head of the Vatican is usually around 570, and so is the Dalai Lama.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And here we have great sages.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We have great names such as Dogen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.66,0:18:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We have Meister Eckhart, who got into his own trouble with the Catholic Church, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.94,0:18:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he was a mystic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.94,0:18:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So even those who are religious are compatible with the religion only to a certain level.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.80,0:18:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And once you get up into the 700s, you may not start having trouble with the ecclesiastic authorities.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Because by the 700s, you've become a mystic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.34,0:18:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So instead of ecclesiastic doctrine, one may now begin speaking of one's own inner knowingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.60,0:18:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In Catholicism, or in Christianity, it's called Unio Mystica.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.60,0:19:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Unio Mystica is the equivalent term for the mystic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.99,0:19:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,As the small self dissolves into the Self with a capital S,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.05,0:19:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the knowingness begins to spring forth from within.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It constitutes the so-called Purusha, the knowingness teacher within the spiritual teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The spiritual teacher no longer speaks from personhood, but from the awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.53,0:19:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So the teacher is speaking of an awareness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher is not talking about himself personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher doesn't even have an interest in himself personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.46,0:19:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The person of the teacher is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.84,0:19:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he never talks about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.17,0:19:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What does he do? He eats breakfast? He takes a nap at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the talk about, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So the illumination comes from within.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.60,0:20:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They then become a mystic.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.60,0:20:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And the highest teachers then are the mystics,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,who go from, let's say, enlightenment is really formally at level 600,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Satchitananda, a state of silent bliss.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And most people that reach that leave then, 50% leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,once they hit that state, because the invitation is open,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's no purpose any further in the physicality.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.53,0:20:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,However, there may be some prior karmic agreement,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and the person may decide to continue on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So, to have anybody on the planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.75,0:20:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,over 600 is rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.75,0:20:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And there are whole centuries, whole centuries,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.75,0:20:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,when there was not one single person on the planet calibrated over 600.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, not one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:20:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, for decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:21:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So these are all, so this is just a different paradigm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.75,0:21:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Emmet Fox, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.09,0:21:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Joel Goldsmith, all the well-known names,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.09,0:21:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Manly Hall, Aldous Huxley,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Karmapa,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.20,0:21:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,that I had a chance to meet myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.20,0:21:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and people whose names I can't read up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.23,0:21:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Brother Lawrence, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the Jesus prayer,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody knows the prayer of Brother Lawrence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.46,0:21:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Just constantly keep the love of God within your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.46,0:21:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a conscious recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.46,0:21:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nisargadatta Maharaj, Ramana Maharshi,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.13,0:21:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,these are 720,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.13,0:21:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,these are recent,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.13,0:21:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,people recently on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.13,0:21:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mutt Kananda, who I also had a chance to meet,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.25,0:21:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,was a very entertaining and fun person to be with.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.25,0:21:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So, alright, so the only reason to point them out
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.64,0:21:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is I wanted to contrast the great scientists,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:21:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,it's very obvious who they are, what they stand for,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.64,0:22:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and how they operate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.64,0:22:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And even though they may personally have a spiritual understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.01,0:22:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and be devoted,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.01,0:22:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,their public life is not the same as these people.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.01,0:22:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,These people, their public life
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.01,0:22:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,was reflected that which they had become.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.01,0:22:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So, now, what's the next slide after that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.25,0:22:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,44?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.94,0:22:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's just more spiritual teachers, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.94,0:22:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just because I wanted you to see
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.94,0:22:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,a whole lot of science over the centuries,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.94,0:22:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,over the centuries,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.94,0:22:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's one paradigm of reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.09,0:22:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And the spiritual people have a different paradigm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.09,0:22:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you see, the scientist is supposedly objective,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.09,0:22:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and he deals with the linear domain,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.09,0:22:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,specifics of the linear domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.09,0:22:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Spirituality went from 500 up,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.09,0:22:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you're dealing with the non-linear domain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.09,0:23:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no longer linear,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.19,0:23:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore, it's no longer provable.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.19,0:23:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not in the realm of provability.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.19,0:23:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So, to apply the rules of science,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.19,0:23:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,which have to do with logical provability,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.45,0:23:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,they have to do with content.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.75,0:23:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual reality has to do with context.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.00,0:23:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot prove context from content.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.00,0:23:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So, all attempts to prove in either direction are futile, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.03,0:23:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Because one is air and one is water, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.80,0:23:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so, here's the pope in 570,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.70,0:23:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the last pope in 570,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.70,0:23:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Father Pio, 585, Plotinus, Huang Po,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.70,0:23:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,who we've discussed a number of times
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.70,0:23:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,when we discussed the void.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.70,0:23:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So, here we have the great names.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.70,0:24:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You recognize them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.70,0:24:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And here's my pal Socrates,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.70,0:24:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,like an old buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.70,0:24:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And Socrates really was a big help in my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.70,0:24:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,and continues to be until today.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.95,0:24:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the white brotherhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.95,0:24:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so, we're all familiar now,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.18,0:24:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've put these in circles,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.18,0:24:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,several books to repeat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.18,0:24:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you see a contrast between two paradigms,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.18,0:24:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the linear, which is science,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.24,0:24:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,the linear, documentable, provable.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.24,0:24:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The non-linear is experiential,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.24,0:24:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,experiential, not provable.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.24,0:24:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,However, now with consciousness research,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.24,0:24:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,it's confirmable.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.24,0:24:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's confirmable, but not provable.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.24,0:24:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, there's something that calibrates at 700,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.24,0:24:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ramana Maharshi or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.24,0:24:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and we know what that means,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.24,0:24:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,because we've used it, like an altimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.24,0:24:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been to so many places with the altimeter,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.24,0:25:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,that we know what 700 means.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.09,0:25:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's confirmatory,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.09,0:25:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's evidentiary,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.09,0:25:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not logical proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.09,0:25:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we'll move to the next one, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.81,0:25:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that say?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.74,0:25:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't read it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.67,0:25:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's see what it says.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.77,0:25:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say this is love.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.25,0:25:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that say?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.25,0:25:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Passion and attraction?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.82,0:25:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's the wrong slide.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.66,0:25:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.66,0:25:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.66,0:25:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.66,0:25:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's brain function.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.98,0:25:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We could do brain function.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.98,0:25:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just do brain function, review that,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.98,0:25:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we'll be done with the review.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.98,0:25:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,23 is brain function.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.98,0:26:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted people to notice that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.44,0:26:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.53,0:26:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you got that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.53,0:26:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.98,0:26:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because spiritual work,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.98,0:26:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,just by your intention and your alignment,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.14,0:26:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,your commitment,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.14,0:26:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,brings up kundalini energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.14,0:26:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,a spiritual energy,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.14,0:26:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,which then creates the etheric brain
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.14,0:26:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and the etheric body.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.14,0:26:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This happens at consciousness level 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.18,0:26:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,From 200 down,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.26,0:26:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the brain is dominated by animal instincts.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.26,0:26:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the world of the ego,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.26,0:26:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's natural,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.29,0:26:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,because they're dominated by that,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.29,0:26:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,think in terms of dominance,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.29,0:26:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.29,0:26:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,getting,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.29,0:26:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,getting even,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.29,0:26:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the alpha male,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.29,0:26:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the wolf pack,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.29,0:26:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,territorial.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.29,0:26:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's today's headlines, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.29,0:26:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The alpha male at the head of a country,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.29,0:26:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,they're all very territorial,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.29,0:26:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,they glare and bare their teeth at everybody else,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.29,0:26:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and so,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.84,0:27:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.84,0:27:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,mankind is still very much
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.84,0:27:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,on the level of the animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.84,0:27:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.84,0:27:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,85% of the population of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.84,0:27:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates below 200.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.09,0:27:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The language of the animal
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.09,0:27:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,makes sense to the populace.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.09,0:27:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I want to be a big man
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.14,0:27:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,in a less evolved,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.90,0:27:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,let's say,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.90,0:27:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,country than this one,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.90,0:27:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to talk about enemies
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.90,0:27:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and hostility
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.90,0:27:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and getting even with people
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.90,0:27:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and annexing people next to me
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.90,0:27:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and capturing people
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.90,0:27:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and killing them,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.90,0:27:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,because that's the language
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.90,0:27:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,of the jungle.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.09,0:27:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the world of the jungle.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.09,0:27:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill or be killed,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.09,0:27:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,territorial,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.09,0:27:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,alpha male against alpha male,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.09,0:27:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,challenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.09,0:27:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and the bearing of the teeth
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.16,0:27:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and the growling.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.16,0:27:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So every night's weekly news
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.50,0:27:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,or evening news
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.50,0:27:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,is the news of the growling.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.74,0:27:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This prime minister said that,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.74,0:27:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,this general said that,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.74,0:27:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,this leader or this president
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.74,0:27:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,of this country said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.74,0:28:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And they all go
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.74,0:28:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,grrr, grrr, grrr, grrr, grrr, grrr,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.74,0:28:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,and then they go,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.74,0:28:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,me bigger you, brr,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.74,0:28:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,me bigger you, brr.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.74,0:28:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, atomic,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.05,0:28:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,ho, ho, homo.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.07,0:28:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, atomic one.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.07,0:28:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We blow up the world
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.46,0:28:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and then our savior will be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.46,0:28:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, the savior just left
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.46,0:28:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,when the world blows up,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.46,0:28:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,not when it doesn't get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.46,0:28:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Time for the saviors before,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.57,0:28:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,not after, folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.57,0:28:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They got everything backward
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.02,0:28:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,in that culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.33,0:28:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, so we see the input
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.36,0:28:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,then goes through the emotional,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.36,0:28:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,fast,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.36,0:28:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it bypasses the prefrontal cortex,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.36,0:28:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,which is man's reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.36,0:28:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and it goes into his emotional reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.36,0:28:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So below 200,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.72,0:28:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,people, everything is,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.72,0:29:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,has to do with how you feel about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.72,0:29:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, when it comes down to reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.00,0:29:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care how anybody feels
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.00,0:29:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.00,0:29:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Tells me they want to feel about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.14,0:29:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,tell your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.14,0:29:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not your grandma,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.14,0:29:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.14,0:29:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,How you feel about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.14,0:29:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,what do I care about your feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.14,0:29:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What do I care about you feel about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.14,0:29:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeling is really narcissistic,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.35,0:29:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.35,0:29:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you get on your blog site
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.35,0:29:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and you blat away how you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.35,0:29:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you talk about free speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.35,0:29:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's my right to say that,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.35,0:29:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.35,0:29:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.15,0:29:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody cares how you feel about it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.78,0:29:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.78,0:29:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.78,0:29:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody really cares
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.81,0:29:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,how you feel about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.81,0:29:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your feelings to yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.07,0:29:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't squish them all over everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.25,0:29:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's my feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.25,0:29:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's my feelings.
