Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.59,0:30:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.59,0:30:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.46,0:30:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you bloggers
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.46,0:30:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,for reminding us
