Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.24,0:31:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Certain things, it says, will not be forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.64,0:31:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you start playing with evil at that level,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.33,0:31:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you're playing in dangerous waters,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.68,0:31:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you can get caught by the current.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.09,0:31:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.75,0:31:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,For one thing, it changes your brain chemistry.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.77,0:31:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You can imagine what your brain chemistry is like
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.85,0:31:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,after you play around with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.77,0:31:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.24,0:31:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So at consciousness level 200, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.40,0:31:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens is the kundalini energy begins to rise.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.79,0:31:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It begins to flow up through the energy system.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.72,0:31:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy chakras.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.35,0:31:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,And, of course, science would probably poo-poo.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.59,0:31:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure science, I never asked science
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.09,0:31:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,whether they think of kundalini energy
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.55,0:31:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,because I didn't want to hear the response.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.20,0:32:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But the kundalini energy that inputs
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.66,0:32:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and begins to shift how you process.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.35,0:32:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you process.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.61,0:32:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, these people do not have an etheric brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.56,0:32:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,They have a collective root consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.73,0:32:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,just like animals do,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.67,0:32:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and certain levels of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.58,0:32:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have an individual etheric brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.57,0:32:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So at level 200, then,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.24,0:32:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the dominance shifts to the other side of the brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.03,0:32:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and you have an etheric brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.92,0:32:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And the information goes very fast
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.66,0:32:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,through your etheric brain,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.90,0:32:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,through your spiritual awareness,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.79,0:32:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and it comes out completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.09,0:32:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.35,0:32:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So two different domains they are, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.74,0:32:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Two different domains.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.51,0:32:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Processing things differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.72,0:32:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Processing things differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.74,0:32:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Processing things differently.
