Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.03,0:32:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming to different conclusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.53,0:32:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So each one actually perceives the world in a different way.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.09,0:32:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually experiences it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.57,0:33:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can't make people wrong for how they experience it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.24,0:33:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How they experience it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.09,0:33:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's how they experience it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.98,0:33:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you're a therapist,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.33,0:33:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you really don't want to know how they experience it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.75,0:33:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I prefer they keep it to themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.38,0:33:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if you calibrate a level of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.36,0:33:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,you can pretty much predict how they're going to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.60,0:33:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So when I see the writer is having to do with science and God,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.30,0:33:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,if you know the calibrated level of the writer,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.91,0:33:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you can pretty much predict exactly what's going to be said.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.54,0:33:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just language is a little different from one to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.97,0:33:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go to the next.
