Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.31,0:33:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.85,0:33:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, circle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.61,0:33:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, no.
