Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.44,0:34:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.48,0:34:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, because we're going to be talking about science versus God,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.44,0:34:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,science versus divinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.78,0:34:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and we saw what science calibrated in the 400s up to 499.
