Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.07,0:51:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,experience because it's beyond experiencing. Because it becomes identity. You only experience
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.48,0:52:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is a duality. There's an experiencer and then there's that which is experienced. That duality
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.57,0:52:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,has to be transcended. There is only that which is, with no division into experiencer and
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.01,0:52:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,experiencer. All right. Consciousness is then the source of life. Divinity is the all-person
